== INSTALL ==
 1.) Windows
 2.) Mac OS X
 3.) Linux
 
== Windows ==

 ?
 
== Mac OS X ==

 Standard compilation (library+examples):
 ----------------------------------------------------
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake ..
 make
 
 
 Develop compilation (library+examples+tests):
 Downloads gtest-1.6.0, if neccessary
 ----------------------------------------------------
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake -DLEMONADE_TESTS=ON ..
 make
 
 Only documentation (By Doxygen):
 ----------------------------------------------------
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake ..
 make docs
 
 Standard compilation of example (lib already build):
 ----------------------------------------------------
 cd path/to/example
 cmake -DLEMONADE_INCLUDE_DIR=/path/to/LeMonADE/ -DLEMONADE_LIBRARY_DIR=/path/to/LeMonADE/ .
 make
 

== Linux ==

 Standard compilation (library+examples):
 ----------------------------------------------------
 ./configure
 make
 
 OR
 
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake ..
 make
 
 
 Develop compilation (library+examples+tests):
 Downloads gtest-1.6.0, if neccessary
 ----------------------------------------------------
 ./configure -DLEMONADE_TESTS=ON
 make
 
 OR
 
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake -DLEMONADE_TESTS=ON ..
 make
 
 Only documentation (By Doxygen):
 ----------------------------------------------------
 ./configure
 make docs
 
 
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake ..
 make docs
 
 Standard compilation of example (lib already build):
 ----------------------------------------------------
 cd path/to/example
 cmake cmake -DLEMONADE_INCLUDE_DIR=/path/to/LeMonADE/ -DLEMONADE_LIBRARY_DIR=/path/to/LeMonADE/ .
 make
 
 
 ----------------------------------------------------
 For additional options for installation or build path
 see Readme.md
